=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">wild lawsuit</a> filed by Brendan Sullivan, a former managing =
director at Archegos, against Archegos, Hwang and a few other Archegos exec=
utives. There is so much good stuff in it =E2=80=94=C2=A0here is a <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28276298.281582/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDctMDUvLWdvZC1od2FuZy1h=
bmQtYXJjaGVnb3Mtc3VpdC1kZXRhaWxzLWlubmVyLXdvcmtpbmdzLW9mLWZpcm0_Y21waWQ9QkJ=
EMDcwNTIyX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZX=
ImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjIwNzA1JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319=
a23cB9881610a/email" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;"> Bloomberg article about it</a>=C2=A0highligh=
ting many wild things that are totally different from the wild things we wi=
ll talk about here=C2=A0=E2=80=94=C2=A0but my favorite part=C2=A0is the acc=
ounting of how much money Sullivan thinks he is owed. The complaint lays ou=
t his bonus each year and how much of it was deferred to be invested into A=
rchegos; I=E2=80=99ll summarize it in a little table[2]:</p><div class=3D"b=
ody-image" style=3D"margin: 20px 0px;">
